---
title: Beef & Pineapple Tacos with Lime Yoghurt
description: Pineapple is a classic ingredient in Mexico – and one bite of these sweet and savoury tacos explains why! The tropical fruit adds a bright, zingy flavour to the salsa, plus the juice makes the mildly spiced beef mixture extra tender.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b721559ae08b54cfc0442f3-2e24bba6.jpg
